# Tender Notice: W7701-247838 Tenax Samplers
## Tender Announcement Details

### Solicitation Number
WS4422824947

### Publication Date
2024-02-07

### Tender Closing Date and Time

### Amendment Number
4

### Expected Contract Start Date
2024-03-15

### Expected Contract End Date
2024-03-15 (2026-03-15 is removed for redundancy)

### Tender Status
The Contract has been Cancelled. Tender no. 4600 Passive Absorption Dosimeter Tenax pads will no longer be pursued.

### Major Items
* UNSPSC: 46180000 - Personal Safety and Protection
* Lead Procuring Entity: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)

### Supporting Facts
* End-User Entity: Department of National Defence (DND)
* Tendering Entity: Defense Research and Development Canada (DRDC) Suffield Research Centre (SRC)
 
### Key Contact Information
* Name: Lee, Oana (SPAC/PSPC)
* Contact Email: <oana.lee@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca>
* Contract and Tender Documents provided on [Ariba Discovery](https://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/18737164?extsite=MTg3MzcxNjRfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)

### Reason for Contract Cancelation
Due to the Contract no longer being valid, a contract-related notice has been **cancelled** as per the previous amendment.

### Closing Comments
The solicitation is no longer valid. As per the Contract specifics all materials needed for submission have been listed.
